  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK766">
<l>maṟamāṉa māṇṭa vaḻiccelavu tēṟṟa</l>
<l>meṉanāṉkē yēmam paṭaikku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Valour, honour, following in the excellent-footsteps (of its predecessors) and trust-worthiness; these four alone constitute the safeguard of an army.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
